1
00:00:37,300 --> 00:00:40,580
=Reincarnated Love=

2
00:00:40,780 --> 00:00:43,700
=Episode 21=

3
00:00:48,350 --> 00:00:49,190
Milady.

4
00:00:57,240 --> 00:00:58,710
Tell the jailer to let

5
00:01:00,390 --> 00:01:03,710
Jiang Wanyue visit Jiang Huaikang.

6
00:01:04,200 --> 00:01:06,510
Milady, why help them?

7
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:07,840
Just do as I say.

8
00:01:09,790 --> 00:01:11,760
Prepare the carriage.

9
00:01:12,023 --> 00:01:13,362
I'm going to the Brocade Workshop.

10
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:14,590
Yes, milady.

11
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:20,000
(Jiang Wanyue,
you're not wicked at heart.)

12
00:01:21,310 --> 00:01:24,760
(You were merely a pawn
of Jiang Huaikang in the past life.)

13
00:01:25,710 --> 00:01:27,950
(Before Lu Huaijin killed him,)

14
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:30,920
(I'll let you see him one last time.)

15
00:01:31,950 --> 00:01:34,000
(It's the least I can do
for our sisterly bond.)

16
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,240
Jiang Huaikang,

17
00:01:53,510 --> 00:01:55,150
you've got a visitor. Hurry up.

18
00:01:57,430 --> 00:01:58,640
What are you doing here?

19
00:02:00,430 --> 00:02:01,270
Father,

20
00:02:01,510 --> 00:02:04,200
I brought you clean clothes
and some food.

21
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,430
You've suffered.

22
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:12,430
I was this close to defeating

23
00:02:12,430 --> 00:02:13,840
Jiang Huai'an.

24
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:18,360
Once he fell, I'd be in charge
of the household.

25
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:19,840
No.

26
00:02:20,310 --> 00:02:22,400
The household
should've been mine all along.

27
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:25,840
But that vile Jiang Ruoli

28
00:02:26,310 --> 00:02:28,710
shattered all my plans.

29
00:02:29,150 --> 00:02:30,310
And you...

30
00:02:31,150 --> 00:02:32,120
What about you?

31
00:02:32,630 --> 00:02:34,150
My dear daughter,

32
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:38,030
all you ever do is cry day and night.

33
00:02:38,430 --> 00:02:40,910
What else are you even capable of?

34
00:02:42,150 --> 00:02:44,310
Father, how could you say that?

35
00:02:46,710 --> 00:02:47,960
If I don't say it,

36
00:02:48,310 --> 00:02:50,190
should I hope you'll save me?

37
00:02:50,710 --> 00:02:52,960
Or count on you
to set things right for me?

38
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:54,840
How did I end up

39
00:02:55,630 --> 00:02:58,000
with a daughter like you?

40
00:02:59,630 --> 00:03:02,240
You even failed

41
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,430
at currying favor with others.

42
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:05,560
Had I known better,

43
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,430
I'd have sent you to the Palace

44
00:03:07,430 --> 00:03:09,910
to be an eunuch's plaything.

45
00:03:15,430 --> 00:03:16,270
Father,

46
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:17,960
as it turned out,

47
00:03:19,150 --> 00:03:21,240
you never saw me as your daughter.

48
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,120
Leave!

49
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,560
I don't want to see you again!

50
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,400
Leave!

51
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:49,000
Isn't this Lady Ruoli?

52
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,630
What a coincidence

53
00:03:50,630 --> 00:03:51,960
to meet you here.

54
00:03:52,910 --> 00:03:54,590
Ms. Zhang, what a surprise.

55
00:03:54,590 --> 00:03:56,000
You recognize me?

56
00:03:56,710 --> 00:03:58,150
Who in the capital doesn't?

57
00:03:58,150 --> 00:03:59,630
You make

58
00:03:59,630 --> 00:04:01,120
the finest unions.

59
00:04:02,030 --> 00:04:03,750
You flatter me.

60
00:04:03,910 --> 00:04:05,400
Come on, have a seat.

61
00:04:07,430 --> 00:04:08,590
Speaking of good fortune,

62
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:11,030
no one compares to you.

63
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:14,800
In the future, you'll surely find

64
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:17,190
a gentleman with true integrity.

65
00:04:18,630 --> 00:04:20,070
You flatter me.

66
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:23,040
Speaking of true integrity,

67
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:26,000
there may be many noble men
in the capital,

68
00:04:26,190 --> 00:04:28,240
but few can truly be called steadfast

69
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:29,510
and devoted to the realm

70
00:04:30,190 --> 00:04:31,390
and its people.

71
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:34,750
Yet, I often hear my father mention

72
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:38,310
that Duke Huo, for instance,

73
00:04:38,430 --> 00:04:39,560
is both wise in governance

74
00:04:39,950 --> 00:04:41,310
and brave in defending the nation,

75
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:43,120
a man truly worthy of the name hero.

76
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,240
Indeed, that's true.

77
00:04:44,430 --> 00:04:46,035
Though I'm but an old woman,

78
00:04:46,046 --> 00:04:47,190
I too have heard the stories

79
00:04:47,190 --> 00:04:49,040
of how the Duke once quelled

80
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:50,360
the unrest around the capital.

81
00:04:50,370 --> 00:04:51,210
Back then,

82
00:04:51,220 --> 00:04:53,630
the Duke drove away those bandits.

83
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:56,430
You know about that?

84
00:04:56,830 --> 00:04:58,000
Of course.

85
00:04:58,390 --> 00:05:00,240
I may not have fought,

86
00:05:00,310 --> 00:05:02,600
but I heard from the people who escaped

87
00:05:02,630 --> 00:05:04,600
that the Duke was quite the strategist.

88
00:05:04,630 --> 00:05:07,120
He surrounded those bandits completely

89
00:05:08,950 --> 00:05:11,070
at some place called Qing...

90
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:12,920
Oh, yes.

91
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:14,070
Qingyang Slope.

92
00:05:14,070 --> 00:05:17,160
Those bandits even cried for mercy.

93
00:05:19,630 --> 00:05:22,070
Duke Huo's bravery needs no praise.

94
00:05:23,390 --> 00:05:27,390
But the common folks
caught in the war truly suffered.

95
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,190
I wonder how the court

96
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:32,160
took care of those poor souls afterward.

97
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:33,830
Lady Ruoli,

98
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,040
don't worry.

99
00:05:35,390 --> 00:05:36,750
When the Duke returned in triumph,

100
00:05:36,830 --> 00:05:37,830
he headed straight

101
00:05:37,830 --> 00:05:39,510
toward the scorched ruins.

102
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:41,390
Seeing the misery

103
00:05:41,390 --> 00:05:42,950
of the weak and sick,

104
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:44,240
he decisively assigned

105
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:47,000
a vast fertile land
below Qingyang Slope,

106
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:49,510
raised funds, gathered craftsmen,

107
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:52,430
built houses, opened farmland,
and sent army physicians.

108
00:05:52,630 --> 00:05:53,720
What's even rarer is

109
00:05:53,750 --> 00:05:56,830
that the Duke made sure
the orphans and widows

110
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:59,310
were properly settled.

111
00:06:03,630 --> 00:06:05,040
After hearing you,

112
00:06:05,750 --> 00:06:08,190
I began to picture the man

113
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:10,040
I'd marry one day,

114
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,000
Tao.

115
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:19,920
Ms. Zhang,

116
00:06:19,950 --> 00:06:23,000
make those bolts of cloth
into new dresses for me.

117
00:06:23,310 --> 00:06:24,630
Rest assured, Lady Ruoli.

118
00:06:24,630 --> 00:06:27,120
Mr. Huo will surely be stunned.

119
00:06:35,950 --> 00:06:36,790
Milady,

120
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:39,190
didn't we come here just to pry

121
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:41,630
into Mr. Lu and Duke Huo's past?

122
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,070
Why did you

123
00:06:43,310 --> 00:06:45,270
suddenly choose Mr. Huo as your husband?

124
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:56,510
Tao, go check the location
below Qingyang Slope.

125
00:06:57,290 --> 00:06:58,580
Find out Duke Huo's work

126
00:06:58,580 --> 00:07:00,390
with the displaced.

127
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:04,830
Focus on the women with kids

128
00:07:04,860 --> 00:07:06,553
who were especially cared
for by the Duke.

129
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:09,120
Remember: No one must suspect a thing.

130
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,320
Yes.

131
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:12,120
I'll handle it flawlessly.

132
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:17,950
(Lu Huaijin,)

133
00:07:17,950 --> 00:07:20,000
(I'll uncover
all that happened in the past.)

134
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:22,830
(I'll crush your lies)

135
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:26,750
(and obsessions piece by piece.)

136
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:32,400
(Yanzhi...)

137
00:07:37,510 --> 00:07:38,350
(No.)

138
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:39,560
(Jiang Ruoli,)

139
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:41,000
(restrain yourself.)

140
00:07:47,830 --> 00:07:48,830
What's wrong?

141
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,680
Miss Jiang, why did you

142
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:52,360
hurry away after you saw me,

143
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,620
pretending not to see me at all?

144
00:07:54,830 --> 00:07:56,000
Was it out of guilt

145
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:58,800
or a grudge against me?

146
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,060
The road lies open before us.

147
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:05,120
Why would I feel guilty?

148
00:08:05,950 --> 00:08:07,160
I have matters to attend to,

149
00:08:07,190 --> 00:08:08,063
so I won't bother you.

150
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,950
If you have pressing business,

151
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,080
please go.

152
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:16,840
Jiang Ruoli,

153
00:08:18,750 --> 00:08:20,000
remember who you are.

154
00:08:21,390 --> 00:08:22,950
My father's matter isn't over.

155
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:26,560
Don't let me catch you scheming
behind my back.

156
00:08:30,390 --> 00:08:32,600
I'll keep your words in mind.

157
00:08:33,790 --> 00:08:34,630
Goodbye.

158
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:41,560
(Yanzhi,)

159
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:43,080
(wait a little longer)

160
00:08:43,390 --> 00:08:44,960
(for the truth to come to light.)

161
00:08:51,390 --> 00:08:52,240
Confess!

162
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:55,320
Chen Guang, the heir
has treated you kindly.

163
00:08:55,510 --> 00:08:56,670
Why would you do this?

164
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:57,680
Confess!

165
00:08:58,600 --> 00:08:59,440
Shitou.

166
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:06,680
Chen Guang,

167
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:10,790
who ordered you to forge
the letter against my father?

168
00:09:16,630 --> 00:09:18,440
Who is this person behind it all?

169
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,550
No one ordered me.

170
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,790
When I was a child,

171
00:09:30,150 --> 00:09:32,030
most of my skills were taught by you.

172
00:09:34,030 --> 00:09:35,443
You served my father for many years,

173
00:09:36,030 --> 00:09:37,440
fighting on countless battlefields,

174
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,840
slaying enemy after enemy.

175
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:45,000
I always saw you as a man
of unyielding honor,

176
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:50,270
who'd never do something like this.

177
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:54,360
My father is old now.

178
00:09:55,630 --> 00:09:57,720
I don't know how long
he can endure in that cell.

179
00:09:59,550 --> 00:10:00,550
Chen Guang,

180
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,910
tell me who the mastermind is.

181
00:10:05,790 --> 00:10:07,030
Once I rescue my father,

182
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:09,790
I'll let this go.

183
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:16,840
Mr. Huo...

184
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:18,720
Mr. Huo,

185
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:23,030
the one who framed the Duke

186
00:10:24,030 --> 00:10:26,840
was indeed someone else.

187
00:10:27,630 --> 00:10:28,480
Who was it?

188
00:10:28,510 --> 00:10:29,350
It was...

189
00:10:29,910 --> 00:10:30,750
It was...

190
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,960
Mr. Huo, this...

191
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,080
He was poisoned to death.

192
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:07,800
Mr. Huo.

193
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:11,030
Just as you said,

194
00:11:11,630 --> 00:11:12,663
Chen Guang has confessed.

195
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:14,360
That's wonderful news.

196
00:11:14,750 --> 00:11:17,080
Duke Huo's name can finally be cleared.

197
00:11:18,150 --> 00:11:19,610
There's one thing I don't understand.

198
00:11:23,510 --> 00:11:24,750
How did you find out

199
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:26,870
about Chen Guang's involvement?

200
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,320
As I told you,

201
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:32,000
it's just my guess.

202
00:11:37,390 --> 00:11:38,230
Jiang Ruoli,

203
00:11:39,630 --> 00:11:40,840
it was so precise,

204
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:42,550
striking right at the heart.

205
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:45,750
Are you sure it's only a guess?

206
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:49,440
Or perhaps,

207
00:11:51,550 --> 00:11:52,670
you're hiding

208
00:11:53,270 --> 00:11:54,960
a secret?

209
00:11:56,790 --> 00:11:57,630
I...

210
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:02,040
Yanzhi.

211
00:12:03,910 --> 00:12:04,750
If I tell you

212
00:12:05,750 --> 00:12:07,600
that everything I did was for you,

213
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,630
would you believe me?

214
00:12:13,670 --> 00:12:14,600
This...

215
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:19,680
Yanzhi,

216
00:12:21,390 --> 00:12:24,220
all I'm doing now is truly for you.

217
00:12:24,220 --> 00:12:25,590
♪The dream shattered♪

218
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,200
I...

219
00:12:27,630 --> 00:12:29,270
♪Like a restless soul♪

220
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:30,600
Yanzhi.

221
00:12:32,110 --> 00:12:33,490
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

222
00:12:33,510 --> 00:12:34,350
Yanzhi,

223
00:12:34,750 --> 00:12:35,590
what's wrong?

224
00:12:37,720 --> 00:12:38,560
Yanzhi.

225
00:12:39,270 --> 00:12:40,110
Yanzhi!

226
00:12:40,390 --> 00:12:41,363
What's happening to you?

227
00:12:41,750 --> 00:12:42,590
Yanzhi...

228
00:12:43,670 --> 00:12:44,510
Yanzhi?

229
00:12:48,590 --> 00:12:50,110
♪When fate falls apart♪

230
00:12:50,510 --> 00:12:54,070
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

231
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:56,320
Who are you?

232
00:12:57,390 --> 00:12:58,390
Why do I feel

233
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:01,840
like I've known you before?

234
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:05,080
Jiang Ruoli,

235
00:13:06,030 --> 00:13:07,390
who are you?

236
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:09,920
Yanzhi,

237
00:13:10,440 --> 00:13:11,280
I...

238
00:13:11,990 --> 00:13:15,030
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

239
00:13:15,190 --> 00:13:16,590
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

240
00:13:16,590 --> 00:13:19,710
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

241
00:13:19,790 --> 00:13:21,110
♪Now shatter apart♪

242
00:13:41,940 --> 00:13:43,460
♪The dream shattered♪

243
00:13:43,820 --> 00:13:45,500
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

244
00:13:45,500 --> 00:13:47,140
♪Like a restless soul♪

245
00:13:48,020 --> 00:13:49,580
♪How vague♪

246
00:13:49,980 --> 00:13:51,500
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

247
00:13:51,500 --> 00:13:53,740
♪A blade of frost in dreams♪

248
00:13:54,540 --> 00:13:57,140
♪Love and hate entwined♪

249
00:13:57,620 --> 00:14:00,460
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

250
00:14:01,100 --> 00:14:05,860
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

251
00:14:06,460 --> 00:14:07,980
♪When fate falls apart♪

252
00:14:08,380 --> 00:14:11,940
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

253
00:14:12,660 --> 00:14:14,220
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

254
00:14:14,620 --> 00:14:18,340
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

255
00:14:19,060 --> 00:14:21,900
♪Life after life♪

256
00:14:22,380 --> 00:14:25,060
♪Fated to meet, but never meant to be♪

257
00:14:25,700 --> 00:14:29,780
♪Still, I refuse to bow or yield♪

258
00:14:29,860 --> 00:14:32,900
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

259
00:14:33,060 --> 00:14:34,460
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

260
00:14:34,460 --> 00:14:37,580
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

261
00:14:37,660 --> 00:14:39,100
♪Now shatter apart♪

262
00:14:39,220 --> 00:14:42,980
♪By fate and karmic ties confined♪

263
00:14:43,700 --> 00:14:46,500
♪Is this fate or calamity♪

264
00:14:46,780 --> 00:14:49,620
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

265
00:14:49,940 --> 00:14:54,340
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

266
00:14:54,580 --> 00:14:57,500
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

267
00:14:57,620 --> 00:15:02,060
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

268
00:15:02,260 --> 00:15:07,980
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

269
00:15:08,420 --> 00:15:11,140
♪This fleeting life feels but a dream♪

270
00:15:11,380 --> 00:15:14,100
♪Sober or indulge♪

271
00:15:14,540 --> 00:15:20,540
♪I only wish to be with you,
with all my heart♪
